cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.AI. 

The paper proposes a deep learning model for material and texture recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The model involves end-to-end learning and joint training, which suggests the use of machine learning techniques (cs.LG). The Encoding Layer is a novel component that generalizes existing encoders, which could be considered a contribution to multimedia (cs.MM). The use of loss functions and feature learning also suggests information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as possible sub-categories.
